description:
"Prime Inspector Os Cara Stauffenberg.
<notes> Anointed the cherub of Helix agents; at Geneva HQ she`s known simply as `Prime.` Single. Age seventy-two, with the looks of a beautiful woman in her late thirties due to ultrahigh resolution WatchMe, a perfect control system, regular antioxidant treatments, and periodic removal of accumulated RNA transcription errors. </notes>" (S.52)
name: Oscar Stauffenberg
